INSTALLATION
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Upload all files except these to your web root:
	* .gitignore
	* resources/*
	* nbproject/*

2. Chmod these dirs to 777
	* app/temp/	(and remove its content)
	* app/log/
	* files/	(create if this folder do not exists)
	* incoming/	(create if this folder do not exists)

3. Ensure that file /app/config.ini is not accessible from web!

4. Connect to your database and create database with structure you find in 
   resources/dump.sql file.

5. Remove libs/Nette and libs/dibi and copy content of resources/minified/ to libs/

6. Edit app/config.ini
   Especially edit variable.key - put random string there (only a-z and A-Z and numbers)
   Set credentials for DB connection just below [production < common] header.
	database.host = "<address>"
	database.username = "<name>"
	database.password = "<password>"
	database.database = "<name-of-database>"

7. Put entry into crontab - call address http://<your-web-address>/files/maintainance?key=<variable-key-in-config-ini> This ensure removing of expired item!

8. Now, your web is ready.

   
